111
00:08:46,246 --> 00:08:48,746
The deceased is the master of this residence,

112
00:08:48,746 --> 00:08:52,546
a man of great wealth, Eisuke Kataoka, age 54.

113
00:08:52,546 --> 00:08:55,546
There's been a great impact to his back.

114
00:08:55,546 --> 00:08:58,546
The most severe wound was on the back of his head,

115
00:08:58,546 --> 00:09:00,746
which we believe to be the fatal wound.

116
00:09:00,746 --> 00:09:04,946
The time of his death can be determined to be 5:55pm.

117
00:09:04,946 --> 00:09:11,746
Everyone here heard Mr. Kataoka's scream and the ladder falling.

118
00:09:11,746 --> 00:09:15,946
Mr. Kataoka was in the middle of playing a game with all of you?

119
00:09:15,946 --> 00:09:18,546
Yes, we were playing hide-and-seek.

120
00:09:18,546 --> 00:09:20,246
We were chasing him.

121
00:09:20,246 --> 00:09:23,146
What a thing to do at your age.

122
00:09:23,146 --> 00:09:24,746
Well...

123
00:09:28,746 --> 00:09:30,746
Was it an accident?

124
00:09:30,746 --> 00:09:34,746
