130
00:09:51,646 --> 00:09:53,746
He asked for it!

131
00:09:53,746 --> 00:09:57,346
It's because he never outgrew playing such a game.

132
00:09:57,346 --> 00:09:59,246
She is Mr. Kataoka's wife.

133
00:09:59,246 --> 00:10:01,746
It seems that he remarried three years ago

134
00:10:01,746 --> 00:10:03,746
