141
00:10:28,646 --> 00:10:31,046
Well, it's a very appropriate way for him to die like this.

142
00:10:31,046 --> 00:10:32,646
What?

143
00:10:32,646 --> 00:10:36,046
Seiya, what happened to your hand?

144
00:10:36,046 --> 00:10:40,246
What? Oh, I hurt it with a guitar string a while ago.

145
00:10:41,246 --> 00:10:43,746
What? But back then, didn't he say...

146
00:10:43,746 --> 00:10:45,046
What happened?

147
00:10:45,046 --> 00:10:47,346
I heard a loud noise.

148
00:10:47,346 --> 00:10:49,746
Seiya, where were you all this time?

149
00:10:49,746 --> 00:10:52,746
What do you mean? I was listening to music in my room all this time.

150
00:10:54,046 --> 00:10:59,446
I'm sorry for causing all of you trouble.

151
00:10:59,446 --> 00:11:02,246
But I wonder if this is really an accident.

152
00:11:02,246 --> 00:11:03,246
What?

153
00:11:03,246 --> 00:11:07,246
Is anything bothering you, Mouri?

154
00:11:07,246 --> 00:11:09,946
When Mr. Kataoka challenges me,

155
00:11:09,946 --> 00:11:12,846
